ikely either be garbage or, at the least, sheerly mediocre for the level. Then promptly smack Yakitzma on the noggin for making these silks into the most annoying thing in EQ, now that LD doesn't kill my summoned goodies. (Summoned bags are now useful. Who knew =P)<br><br>Arcale Vi'Cace<br>Lord of the Bad Invis<br>"Buying Yew Leaves and Drake Eggs"<br>"I have 2 Leaves, sell em to you for 200pp"<br>/sigh<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
